installation:

system dependencies:

* sbcl >= 1.0.13
* cairo
* opengl
* freetype
* glut

lisp dependencies:

* cffi (through asdf-install)
* metabang-bind (through-asdf-install)
* cl-opengl from svn://erleuchtet.org/cl-opengl-thomas
* cl-cairo from svn://erleuchtet.org/cl-cairo
* infpre from svn://erleuchtet.org/infpre
* toolbox from svn://erleuchtet.org/toolbox
* vektor from svn://erleuchtet.org/vektor

currently you have to start your lisp from within the perfectstorm directory. this will be fixed.

after loading: (asdf:oos 'asdf:load-op :perfectstorm)
run (storm:storm)

key/mouse-bindings:
* wasd - scroll
* mouse-wheel or +/- - zoom
* v - toggle shaders
* h - toggle health bars
* ` or ^ - developer console :D
* f - (fake)fullscreen
* esc - quit
